{"word":"ἐξέτασις","slug":"ἐξέτασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξέτασις</b></el> <el>(ἐξέτᾰσις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐξετάζω'><el>ἐξετάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a close examination, scrutiny, review</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a military inspection</i> or <i>review</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}